INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I''ve had many cases of love that were just infatuation, but this hate I feel\r\nfor you is the real thing.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You''re the best at all you do -- and all you do is make people hate you.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'In the dictionary under the word, "stupid," it says, "see him."');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'We know you could not live without us. We''ll pay for the funeral.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'We do not complain about your shortcomings, but about your long sayings.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Don''t you realize that there are enough people to hate in the world already \r\nwithout your working so hard to give us another?');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'The thing that terrifies me the most is that someone might hate me as much \r\nas I loathe you.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'When you get run over by a car, it shouldn''t be listed under accidents.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'We hear you are a lady killer. They take one look at you and die of fright!!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'We heard that when you ran away from home your folks sent you a note saying, \r\n"Do not come home and all will be forgiven".');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You have a good family tree, but the crop is a failure.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I don''t consider you a vulture. I consider you something a vulture would \r\neat.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Is your name Amazon? You`re so wide at the mouth.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You are a man who always sticks by his convictions. You will remain a fool \r\nno matter how much you get ridiculed for it!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'A dope you are and dope will remain.\r\nCompletely unlike cocaine.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You add to, not diminish, pain!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'We know that you would go to the end of the world for us. But would you stay \r\nthere?');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Your family tree is good, but you are the sap.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'We all spring from apes, but you didn''t spring far enough.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'It cost me five thousand dollars to look up your family history. A thousand \r\nto look it up and four thousand to hush it up.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Lets play house. You be the door and I''ll slam you.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I hear you are a real humanitarian. You have kept three or four detectives \r\nworking regularly.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I hear you are connected to the Police Department -- by a pair of handcuffs.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Hello -- tall, dark and obnoxious!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You remind me of the ocean -- you make me sick.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You should have been born in the Dark Ages; you look terrible in the light.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'All of your ancestors must number in the millions; it''s hard to believe \r\nthatmany people are to blame for producing you.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Ever since I saw you in your family tree, I''ve wanted to cut it down.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I hear that when you were a child your mother wanted to hire someone to take \r\ncare of you, but the Mafia wanted too much.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'They just invented a new coffin just for you that goes over the head. It''s \r\nfor people who are dead from the neck up.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'After hearing you talk, I now know that the dead do contact us.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You are so two-faced that any woman who married you would be married to a \r\nbigamist.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I always wanted to be a trouble-shooter, but now I see you are not worth it!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'For two cents, I`d give you a piece of my mind -- and all of yours.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You are the only person I''ve ever met whose mind is filthy and sterile at \r\nthe same time!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You have no trouble making ends meet. Your foot is always in your mouth!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I heard you went to see the doctor and told him that you wanted a little \r\nwart removed; so he had you thrown out of his office.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I think Mother Nature really hates you because you remind her so much of all \r\nher mistakes!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You must be the arithmetic man -- you add trouble, subtract pleasure, divide \r\nattention, and multiply ignorance.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Some people are has-beens. You are a never-was.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You started at the bottom -- and it''s been downhill ever since.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You are so boring that you can''t even entertain a doubt.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I don''t mind that you are talking so long as you don''t mind that I''m not \r\nlistening.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I heard that you were born, your father threw rocks at the stork.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I used to think that you were a big pain in the neck. Now I have a much \r\nlower opinion of you.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You must have gotten up on the wrong side of the cage this morning.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I would ask you how old you are, but I know you can''t count that high.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'In the next life, you''ll blaze a way for us.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You are master in your own house -- the doghouse!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'When you die, I''d like to go to your funeral, but I''ll probably have to go \r\nto work that day. I believe in business before pleasure.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You make me believe in reincarnation. Nobody can be as stupid as you in one \r\nlifetime.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Believe me, I don''t want to make a monkey out of you. Why should I take all \r\nthe credit?');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I hear you are very kind to animals, so please give that face back to the \r\ngorilla.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Keep talking. I always yawn when I''m interested.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Some day you will find yourself -- and wish that you hadn''t.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'People clap when they see you -- their hands over their eyes or ears.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Whatever is eating you -- must be suffering horribly.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Why don''t you go to the library and brush up on your ignorance?');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I hear you changed your mind! What did you do with the diaper?');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You have an inferiority complex -- and it''s fully justified.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You are not as bad as people say -- you are worse!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Do you have to leave so soon? I was about to poison the tea.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I''m busy now. Can I ignore you some other time?');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Whom am I calling "stupid"? I don''t know. What''s your name?');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Take a vacation; go to Club Dead.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Your mouth is getting too big for your muzzle.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You are as strong as an ox and almost as intelligent.');
