INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'The stupid person''s idea of a clever person.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'It is only too easy to catch people''s attention by doing something worse \r\nthan anyone else has dared to do it before."\r\nIf you were orphaned when you were a child, I feel sorry for you, but not \r\nfor your parents.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'If you don''t want to give people a bad name, you will have your children \r\nillegitimately.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Is your name Laryngitis? You''re a pain in the neck.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Is your name Dan Druff? You get into people''s hair.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I hear you pick your friends -- to pieces!!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I bet your brain feels as good as new, seeing that you''ve never used it.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'They say that two heads are better than one. In your case, one would have \r\nbeen better than none.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You should toss out more of your funny remarks; that''s all they''re good for.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'People can''t say that you have absolutely nothing! After all, you have \r\ninferiority!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You must have a low opinion of people if you think they''re your equals.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I wish you were all here. I don''t like to think there is more!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'If we were to kill everybody who hates you, it wouldn''t be murder; it would \r\nbe genocide!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Even your best friend cheats on you and lies to you, and that''s the best \r\nfriend you can get.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I don''t think you are a fool. But then, what''s my own humble opinion against \r\nthousands of others?');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Nobody says that you are dumb. They just say you were sixteen years old \r\nbefore you learned how to wave goodbye.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'People say that you are the perfect idiot. I say that you are not perfect, \r\nbut you are doing alright.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Ordinarily people live and learn. You just live.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'The mind reader had a very busy day today reading minds. You were a vacation \r\nfor him.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I thought of you all day today when I was at the zoo.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'When you talk, other people get hoarse just listening.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I would say that you are barking up the wrong tree, but that is your natural \r\nvoice.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I reprimanded my brother for mimicking you. I told him not to act like a \r\nfool.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I''m very careful of how I express my opinions of you because I want to put \r\nas much vituperation in them as possible.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I don''t hold your behavior against you because I realize it was caused by \r\nchildhood trauma; your parents spanked you when you fell on your head and \r\nbroke the cement.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Would you like to replace my business partner who died this morning? I''ll \r\narrange it with the undertaker.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'People say that you are outspoken, but not by anyone that I know of.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Your conversation is like the waves of the sea. It makes me sick!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'We can always tell when you are lying. Your lips move.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'When you get to the men`s room, you will see a sign that says, "Gentlemen." ');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Pay no heed to it. Go right on in.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'The only things you ever make are mistakes and cigarette ashes.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You always manage to keep your neck above water. We can tell by the color of \r\nit.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'All that you are you owe to your parents. Why don''t you send them a penny \r\nand square the account?');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I heard you have hair on your chest, and that`s not your only resemblance to \r\nRin Tin Tin.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'No one should be punished for accident of birth, but you look too much like \r\na wreck not to be.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'There was something about you that I liked, but you spent it.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Sit down and give your mind a rest.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I heard you got a brain transplant and the brain rejected you!');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I think you should live for the moment. But after that, I doubt I''ll think \r\nso.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Man alive! But I wish you weren''t.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I believe in respect for the dead; in fact, I could only respect you if you \r\nWERE dead.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'Is your name Maple Syrup? It should be, you sap.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You spent so much time trying to get rid of that halitosis that you had only \r\nto find out that you are not popular anyway.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'You are the kind of person who, when one first meets you, one doesn''t like \r\nyou. But when one gets to know you better, one hates you.\r\nWe know that romance brings out the beast in you -- the jackass.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I''m looking forward to the pleasure of your company since I haven''t had it \r\nyet.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'There are several people in this world that I find obnoxious and you are all \r\nof them.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'All of your girlfriends kiss you with their eyes closed. Considering your \r\nface, that''s the only way they could.');
INSERT INTO insults VALUES ('', 'I hear that when your mother first saw you, she decided to leave you on the \r\nfront steps of a police station while she turned herself in.');
